{#
  to-main-menu component
  ----------------------
  Compact return path back to the archive gateway. Mirrors PJLM's
  floating "to main menu" link in spirit (lyrics-smiths.htm and similar
  detail pages), but implemented as a static CSS-positioned block rather
  than a JS-driven floating div. Always present on inner pages.
#}
<aside class="to-main-menu" aria-label="Return to archive gateway">
  <a class="to-main-menu__link" href="{{ '/' | url }}">&larr; to main menu</a>
</aside>
